{"tid":2068119,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"曾幾何時，香港電視廣告有過好短既光輝時期","createTime":"2020-06-17T12:17:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T17:02:27.000Z","uid":35457,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ae7e943b0ad347d4b89e7a5b0aa7b9283bb70e37","tid":2068119,"uid":35457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T12:17:27.000Z","msg":"曾幾何時，香港電視廣告有過好短既光輝時期<br />\n不論係政府定係商業廣告都比依家既高汁好多<br />\n依家既政府廣告完全係無營養既洗腦宣傳<br />\n我地罷買TVB既同時，佢就入哂TVB的空檔狂播<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次呢條片我會同大家講下幾個我細個好鐘意既電視廣告<br />\n係國安法通過之後，呢啲廣告亦只能夠成為香港人既回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TL7BxD2v-dM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTL7BxD2v-dM&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wSYtkWzW%2FBkyQE6eFpzr100%3D&h=4c475014\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TL7BxD2v-dM</a><br />\nps.依家YouTube真係追得好嚴<br />\n只要條片同國安法有關都會黃標你<br />\n希望大家都幫手支持下我同埋其他YouTube創作者既Channel <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a1d347435762da3e9aa1f25d4b4b14a62de24f5","tid":2068119,"uid":79382,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T12:57:43.000Z","msg":"第一眼以為你講HKTV，<br />\n跟住諗起嗰陣睇警界線結果，<br />\n俾個亂入嘅麥樂雞廣告嚇撚死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd3c041a55fcee7403d7343bb1a285930fd2248","tid":2068119,"uid":35457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a1d347435762da3e9aa1f25d4b4b14a62de24f5","tid":2068119,"uid":79382,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T12:57:43.000Z","msg":"第一眼以為你講HKTV，<br />\n跟住諗起嗰陣睇警界線結果，<br />\n俾個亂入嘅麥樂雞廣告嚇撚死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal